					</div>
					
					<div class="contact-form-section">
						<h2>About Our Content</h2>
						<p>At SomaDhanTech, we're passionate about sharing knowledge and helping developers, entrepreneurs, and tech enthusiasts succeed in the digital world. Our content covers:</p>
						<ul>
							<li>Web Development Tutorials</li>
							<li>Hosting Solutions & Reviews</li>
							<li>Digital Product Development</li>
							<li>Technology Insights & Trends</li>
							<li>Programming Best Practices</li>
						</ul>
						
						<div class="cta-section">
							<h3>Stay Updated</h3>
							<p>Follow us on social media to get notified about new articles, tutorials, and insights. Join our growing community of developers and tech enthusiasts!</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>
		
		<Footer />
		<GoToTop />
		<HeaderScript />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 2rem;
	}
	
	.contact-page {
		padding: 6rem 0;
		min-height: 80vh;
	}
	
	.contact-header {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}
	
	.contact-header h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		color: var(--text-color);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--text-color) 0%, var(--accent) 100%);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
	}
	
	.contact-header p {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}
	
	.contact-content {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 4rem;
		align-items: start;
	}
	
	.contact-info h2,
	.contact-form-section h2 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--text-color);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	
	.contact-info p,
	.contact-form-section p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}
	
	.social-links {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1rem;
	}
	
	.social-link {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1rem;
		padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		background: var(--bg-secondary);
		color: var(--text-color);
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		border: 2px solid transparent;
	}
	
	.social-link:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
		border-color: var(--accent);
	}
	
	.social-link.twitter:hover {
		background: rgba(29, 161, 242, 0.1);
		color: #1da1f2;
	}
	
	.social-link.github:hover {
		background: rgba(51, 51, 51, 0.1);
		color: #333;
	}
	
	.social-link.linkedin:hover {
		background: rgba(0, 119, 181, 0.1);
		color: #0077b5;
	}
	
	.social-link.facebook:hover {
		background: rgba(24, 119, 242, 0.1);
		color: #1877f2;
	}
	
	.social-link svg {
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}
	
	.social-link span {
		font-weight: 600;
	}
	
	.contact-form-section ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}
	
	.contact-form-section li {
		padding: 0.5rem 0;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		position: relative;
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
	}
	
	.contact-form-section li::before {
		content: 'âœ“';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: var(--accent);
		font-weight: bold;
	}
	
	.cta-section {
		background: var(--bg-secondary);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
	}
	
	.cta-section h3 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--text-color);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	
	.cta-section p {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}
	
	/* Mobile Responsive */
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.contact-page {
			padding: 4rem 0;
		}
		
		.contact-header h1 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}
		
		.contact-content {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 3rem;
		}
		
		.social-link {
			padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
		}
		
		.social-link span {
			font-size: 0.9rem;
		}
	}
	
	@media (max-width: 480px) {
		.container {
			padding: 0 1rem;
		}
		
		.contact-header h1 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}
		
		.contact-header p {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}
		
		.contact-info h2,
		.contact-form-section h2 {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
		}
		
		.cta-section {
			padding: 1.5rem;
		}
	}
</style>